claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table listing contraindications and precautions for various influenza vaccines, including egg-based IIV or LAIV, cell culture–based inactivated vaccines (ccIIV), and recombinant influenza vaccine (RIV). does not support the claim because the table only addresses contraindications and precautions for different flu vaccines and does not provide data on antigenic match with WHO- or FDA-selected strains.
